name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dialoqbase Lite - A SidePanel & Web UI for AI Models

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dialoqbase Lite is a SidePanel & Web UI for AI Models. It allows you to interact with AI models in a conversational way.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Dialoqbase Lite is a simple web UI and copilot for your browsing. It supports most of the AI providers. 
Repo: https://github.com/n4ze3m/dialoqbase-lite.git 
Current Features: 
- Copilot for browsing tasks 
- Support for vision models 
- A minimal Web UI 
- Internet search 
- Chat with PDF on Copilot (side panel)
